OL,3,C'Landmark' for UK lithium production
OL,4,Cas demo plant opens in Cornwall
OL,6,FA demonstration facility in Cornwall
OL,7,Fis set to start producing lithium
OL,8,Fhydroxide - a key ingredient in
OL,9,Fbatteries for electric cars and other
OL,10,Ftech.
OL,12,FThe UK currently imports all of the
OL,13,Flithium it uses, despite being home to
OL,14,F"one of the largest lithium resources
OL,15,Fin Europe".
OL,17,FBut Cornish Lithium hopes to producing
OL,18,F10,000 tonnes of lithium a year by
OL,19,F2027 - and the firm is hailing a new
OL,20,Fdemonstration facility as a "landmark"
OL,21,Fmoment for the project.
