OL,3,C'Landmark' for UK lithium production
OL,4,Cas demo plant opens in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe demo plant in St Austell will use
OL,7,Fgranite from an old China clay pit to
OL,8,Ftest the viability of extracting
OL,9,Flithium from Cornish rock.
OL,11,FIt is hoped the first lithium samples
OL,12,Fwill be sent to car manufacturers in
OL,13,FNovember.
OL,15,FCornish Lithium chief executive Jeremy
OL,16,FWrathall said: "Lithium is critically
OL,17,Fimportant to the manufacturing of
OL,18,Felectric vehicles, grid scale
OL,19,Felectricity storage and rechargeable
OL,20,Findustrial and consumer electronics.
