OL,6,F"We're home to the largest lithium
OL,7,Fresource in Europe with enough beneath
OL,8,Four feet in Cornwall to supply over
OL,9,Fhalf of what the electric vehicle
OL,10,Findustry needs.
OL,12,F"This is a huge untapped advantage
OL,13,Fthat is currently being wasted, when
OL,14,Fit could be making our industries more
OL,15,Fcompetitive and resilient to global
OL,16,Fsupply chain volatility."
