OL,6,FHe said extracting lithium in the UK
OL,7,Fis "sensible" given the geology of
OL,8,FCornwall is right for it, adding it
OL,9,Falso delivers economic and strategic
OL,10,Fsecurity.
OL,12,FHe said producing it on home soil will
OL,13,Fcut emissions from shipping lithium
OL,14,Fabroad and from processing, with the
OL,15,Fplant next to the quarry extracting
OL,16,Flithium from minerals using acid,
OL,17,Frather than roasting with fossil fuels
OL,18,Fwhich is used for most Chinese hard
OL,19,Frock extraction.
