OL,3,C'Landmark' for UK lithium production
OL,4,Cas demo plant opens in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe #50million demonstration plant is
OL,7,Fbeing hailed as a "landmark" for the
OL,8,FUK's transition to green power by
OL,9,FCornish Lithium.
OL,11,FIf successful, the firm will scale up
OL,12,Fthe demo site to a #230million full
OL,13,Fproduction facility.
OL,15,FCornish Lithium estimates the project
OL,16,Fwill contribute #800million and create
OL,17,Fmore than 300 jobs in Cornwall from
OL,18,F2027.
