OL,6,FBusiness and Trade Secretary Jonathan
OL,7,FReynolds said: "This is great news for
OL,8,FCornish Lithium, and will not only
OL,9,Fsupport high-skilled jobs in the South
OL,10,FWest but give a major boost to our
OL,11,Fcritical minerals supply chains for
OL,12,Fthe long term.
OL,14,F"Lithium will be vital to our
OL,15,Fautomotive sector's EV transition and
OL,16,Fdriving the green industries of the
OL,17,Ffuture, which is why we've made clean
OL,18,Fenergy a priority sector in our
OL,19,Fambitious, modern Industrial Strategy."
